In other words, what we think
of as an isolated region today,

00:35:57.100 --> 00:36:02.340
landlocked, and all that, it-- its
significance then was precisely

00:36:02.340 --> 00:36:04.890
because of its centrality.

00:36:04.890 --> 00:36:06.970
They were trading with everyone.

